-- slice 10: a C-constructed Option (reserved ADT tag) round-trips through a Medaka
-- `match`.  charFromCode builds `Some (Char)` in C (runtime mdk_some / MDK_TAG_SOME);
-- the match tests the SAME reserved tag (cellTag → reservedTag) and binds the Char,
-- so charCode 65 = 65.  Proves the BOXED reserved tag + field extraction end-to-end.
main = match charFromCode 65
  Some c => charCode c
  None => 0 - 1
